settings.title: Strøm Tørre Ting
settings.text:
Gryning lar deg strømme frokostvarer til ditt tørrskap hver måned.

Vi tilbyr et utvalg av smakfulle, kjente, noen ganger lokale, bærekraftige tørre varer til din husholdning. Velg kaffe, granola, grøt, havre, syltetøy eller juice og bygg din egen månedlige tørre strøm.

settings.zig-zag_a__text:
We believe that the road to sustainability starts with it being cheap and easy. That is why we offer well-known goods, delivered predictably at good prices as the world's first electricity service for dry household goods.
How many items do you just always want in the closet? We solve this first, so we can improve the sustainability of transport, packaging and food waste in our value chain, while contributing to more family time and better and positive eating habits in your family.
Our suppliers support our vision, but most of all they like loyal customers who buy again, so we can offer you very good prices.
Our vision is ambitious so we want committed members on the team. Become a member now, your membership covers our extra costs of circularity and sustainability.
You save the membership on your first stream from us!

settings.counter2: Kilo mindre å bære fra butikken

settings.zig-zag_a__text:
Streaming physical goods is something completely new, but really very simple.
You build a stream of goods that you want to always have in place. We make sure you never get too much.
You can adjust your power down to 0, - or up to your budget throughout the month. We remind you of the adjustment before we send, and then exactly what you need will come to your home!
You choose a budget of NOK 500 or NOK 1,000 so you always have control over the costs of your electricity. You never pay for more than the goods you receive delivered.
